OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780600263
OL,3,CGovernment commit to stronger safe
OL,4,Csleep protections after Campaign for
OL,5,CGigi
OL,7,FThe government has committed to
OL,8,Ftightening safety rules in nurseries
OL,9,Fafter a campaign by the bereaved
OL,10,Fparents of Genevieve Meehan.
OL,12,FGenevieve, known as Gigi, died at nine-
OL,13,Fmonths-old after being left face down
OL,14,Fon a beanbag at a nursery in Cheadle
OL,15,FHulme, in Stockport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780600263
OL,3,CGovernment commit to stronger safe
OL,4,Csleep protections after Campaign for
OL,5,CGigi
OL,7,FFollowing her death, her parents -
OL,8,FKatie and John - hand delivered a
OL,9,Fletter to Number 10 calling for legal
OL,10,Fchanges to help prevent similar
OL,11,Ftragedies in the future in January
OL,12,F2026.
OL,14,FThey are pushing for mandatory CCTV,
OL,15,Fmore frequent inspections for
OL,16,Fnurseries, and clear, statutory safe
OL,17,Fsleep guidance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780600263
OL,3,CGovernment commit to stronger safe
OL,4,Csleep protections after Campaign for
OL,5,CGigi
OL,7,FThe Minister for Early Education
OL,8,FOlivia Bailey MP has confirmed that
OL,9,Fupdated safer sleep wording -
OL,10,Fdeveloped with experts including The
OL,11,FLullaby Trust and agreed with Ofsted -
OL,12,Fwill take effect from September 2026.
OL,14,FIt comes as she, and His Majesty's
OL,15,FChief Inspector Sir Martyn Oliver,
OL,16,Fpublished letters setting out the
OL,17,Fsteps being taken in response to the
OL,18,FCampaign for Gigi.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780600263
OL,3,CGovernment commit to stronger safe
OL,4,Csleep protections after Campaign for
OL,5,CGigi
OL,7,FOfsted also pledged that safer
OL,8,Fsleeping arrangements will now be
OL,9,Fassessed at every inspection of every
OL,10,Fearly years setting in England.
OL,12,FNursery deputy manager Kate Roughley,
OL,13,Fwas found guilty of killing Genevieve
OL,14,Fand jailed for 14 years in May 2024.
OL,16,FCCTV captured the nine-month-old
OL,17,Fstruggling to breath after being
OL,18,Ftightly swaddled and strapped face
OL,19,Fdown on a beanbag for more than an
OL,20,Fhour and a half at Tiny Toes nursery
OL,21,Fin, Stockport, in May 2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
