PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780600263
OL,3,CGovernment commit to stronger safe
OL,4,Csleep protections after Campaign for
OL,5,CGigi
OL,7,FIn a statement they said: "We are
OL,8,Fimmensely proud of Gigi and the
OL,9,Fchanges being made in her name.
OL,10,FKnowing that Ofsted inspectors will
OL,11,Fnow receive safer sleep training, work
OL,12,Fwith strengthened inspection tools and
OL,13,Fguidance, and assess sleep provision
OL,14,Fat every single inspection is a
OL,15,Fsignificant step forward in the
OL,16,Fcampaign.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780600263
OL,3,CGovernment commit to stronger safe
OL,4,Csleep protections after Campaign for
OL,5,CGigi
OL,7,F"We are grateful to Sir Martyn Oliver
OL,8,Fand Minister Bailey for their time and
OL,9,Fcommitment. While this milestone is
OL,10,Fimportant, our work is not yet
OL,11,Fcomplete.
OL,13,F"We remain determined to keep pushing
OL,14,Funtil every ask of Campaign for Gigi
OL,15,Fhas been delivered.
OL,17,F"We are deeply grateful to everyone
OL,18,Fwho has supported us throughout this
OL,19,Fjourney. Every step forward is part of
OL,20,FGigi's legacy."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
