OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780600263
OL,3,CGovernment commit to stronger safe
OL,4,Csleep protections after Campaign for
OL,5,CGigi
OL,7,FSir Martyn Oliver wrote personally to
OL,8,FKatie and John to confirm that
OL,9,FOfsted's updated Early Years
OL,10,FInspection Toolkit now sets out
OL,11,Fclearer expectations around safer
OL,12,Fsleep, particularly for babies and
OL,13,Fchildren under two.
OL,15,FKate Holmes, Head of Support and
OL,16,FInformation at The Lullaby Trust,
OL,17,Fsaid: "The Lullaby Trust has worked
OL,18,Fclosely with the Department for
OL,19,FEducation to assist with the
OL,20,Fdevelopment of the updated wording in
OL,21,Fthe new EYFS framework.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780600263
OL,3,CGovernment commit to stronger safe
OL,4,Csleep protections after Campaign for
OL,5,CGigi
OL,7,F"This is a significant milestone for
OL,8,Fbaby safety and for the Campaign for
OL,9,FGigi. Every baby and young child
OL,10,Fdeserves to sleep as safely as
OL,11,Fpossible in every childcare setting.
OL,13,F"By strengthening safer sleep
OL,14,Frequirements within EYFS statutory
OL,15,Fframework, the Government is taking a
OL,16,Fvital step forward to making this
OL,17,Freality.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780600263
OL,3,CGovernment commit to stronger safe
OL,4,Csleep protections after Campaign for
OL,5,CGigi
OL,7,F"The commitment from Ofsted to assess
OL,8,Fsafer sleep practices on every
OL,9,Finspection will help ensure that
OL,10,Fguidance is not just written down, but
OL,11,Fgenuinely understood and followed. We
OL,12,Fare grateful to Katie and John for
OL,13,Ftheir tireless campaigning in Gigi's
OL,14,Fname.
OL,16,F"Gigi's legacy will help protect
OL,17,Fbabies and young children for years to
OL,18,Fcome."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
