PN,39812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780600263
OL,3,CGovernment commit to stronger safe
OL,4,Csleep protections after Campaign for
OL,5,CGigi
OL,7,FCheadle MP Tom Morrison said: "Katie
OL,8,Fand John have shown extraordinary
OL,9,Fcourage and determination in turning
OL,10,Fthe most devastating loss imaginable
OL,11,Finto a campaign that will protect
OL,12,Fchildren across the country.
OL,14,F"These commitments from the Minister
OL,15,Fand from Sir Martyn Oliver represent
OL,16,Freal, tangible progress. Safer sleep
OL,17,Fguidance will now be explicit in law,
OL,18,Fand inspectors will check compliance
OL,19,Fon every single visit to an early
OL,20,Fyears setting.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
