OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780600263
OL,3,CGovernment commit to stronger safe
OL,4,Csleep protections after Campaign for
OL,5,CGigi
OL,7,F"That is a direct result of this
OL,8,Fcampaign. I am proud to have supported
OL,9,FKatie and John, and I will continue to
OL,10,Fpush for every remaining ask of the
OL,11,FCampaign for Gigi to be delivered in
OL,12,Ffull."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
